    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs ẜazzija schohs\nedsedams: Schee irr Deewa Kar-\na-Spehks/un nofauze tahs Wee-\nas Wahrdü Mâinaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "si/ pee Eesawu / un wiꞥſch tew\narridsan eet pretti/un tſchetrsfinits\nWihrí ar winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad bihjajabs Jehkahs toh-\nti / un winnam bija bail / un\nſchkibretohs Laudis/kas tam bij/\nun tahs Awis/ un tohs Wehr-\nſchus/ un tohs Kameetus/ diwe-\njös Pulkôs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ẜazzija : Ja Eesaws\nweenam Pulkam wirſtu nahks/\nun apkaus to / tad tas ohtrs\nPulks isnnuks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs ẜazzija : Deews\nmanna Tehwa Ahbrâdina / un\ntu Deews manna Tehwa Jhsa-\naka. Ak KUNGS! kas tu us\nmanni ẜazzijis effi/ atgreeſees us\ntawu Semmi / un us tawcem\nRaddeem/ un es tew gribbu labb\ndarriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es esmu mas prett wiſ-\nfahm Apschehloschanahm / un\nprett wiſfas Peetizzibas / ko tu\ntawam Kalpam darrijis effi. Jo\nar ſcho Speeki esmu es pahr ſcho\nJardanu pahrgahjis/ un nu ef-\nmu es par diwi Pulkeem tapvis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Iſpesti mann/ luhdsams/\nno manna Brahta Rohkas / no\nEesawa Rohkas / jo es bihstohe\npar winnu / ka tas ne nahk un\napkanj mann/ to Mahti ar teem\nBehrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu effi ẜazzijis: Es ne\nmitteſchohs tew labdarriht/un liſ-\nſchu tawu Dſimmumu/ ka Juh-\nxas Smiltis / kas preeſch leela\nPulka ne warr iſſkatitas tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch palikke tur to\nMak-\n"
    }
